---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact — Notes Automate" description="Get in touch with Notes Automate. Email us with feedback, corrections, partnership inquiries, or questions about Obsidian plugins, note-taking workflows, second brain systems.">
  <article class="contact">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="lead">We read every email. Typical response time: <strong>2–4 business days</strong>.</p>

    <h2>📩 Email us</h2>
    <p>For all inquiries, write to:</p>
    <p class="email-block"><a href="mailto:hello@notes-automate.com">hello@notes-automate.com</a></p>

    <h2>What to include</h2>
    <p>To help us respond quickly, please mention in your subject line:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>[Correction]</strong> — if you spotted a factual error in an article</li>
      <li><strong>[Suggestion]</strong> — topic ideas, missing tools/products to cover</li>
      <li><strong>[Partnership]</strong> — guest posts, sponsorships, brand partnerships</li>
      <li><strong>[Privacy]</strong> — GDPR/CCPA data requests (see <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
      <li><strong>[Other]</strong> — anything else</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we cover</h2>
    <p>Obsidian plugins, note-taking workflows, second brain systems. We are most useful for questions in those areas. For unrelated topics, we may not be the right resource — but feel free to ask anyway.</p>

    <h2>What we don't do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Paid product placements (we keep editorial independent).</li>
      <li>Free product reviews on demand (we choose what to cover based on reader interest).</li>
      <li>Custom consulting on your specific setup (we publish general guides only).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Response times</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Corrections: usually within 24 hours</li>
      <li>Privacy requests: within 30 days (GDPR/CCPA timeline)</li>
      <li>Partnerships: 2–4 business days</li>
      <li>General feedback: when we get to it (we read everything)</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #1f2937; }
  .contact h1 { font-size: 2.1rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .contact .lead { color: #4b5563; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .contact h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; }
  .contact ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  .contact li { margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .contact a { color: #2563eb; text-decoration: underline; }
  .email-block { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1.05rem; margin: .5rem 0 1rem; }
  .email-block a { font-weight: 600; }
</style>
